snippet.title: Volcano Climber
snippet.description:
The lava is coming fast, keep climbing!

Simple touch mechanics, challenging obstacles and a retro arcade feel... 

An explorer inside an infinite volcano full of coins, items and tricky platforms. And all he's got is his less-than-optimal jetpack! Better than nothing!

Volcano Climber is an infinite arcade game for iOS and Android.

Learn more: volcanoclimber.com

PLAY FOR FREE:

iOS: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/volcano-climber/id1229133772

Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.spokgames.volcanoclimber
